## Introduction
TowerWarZ is a fully open-source Tower Defense Game. ~~It is created because of the lack of open source games~~ It is created **out of boredom and the fact that most tower defense games don't fit us**

### Copyrights
As this is FREE SOFTWARE, we do not restrict you to anything, but please credit us if you are releasing another version of this

Thank you!
